	<h3>{l s='How can i display CMS page content' mod='opartajaxpopup'}</h3>
	{l s='Copy this example where you want then edit it with your values' mod='opartajaxpopup'}:<br />
	<div style="padding: 10px; margin: 10px; border: 1px solid #CCCED7; background: #FFF;">
		&lt;a href="#" onClick="showOpartAjaxPopup(<span style="color:red; font-weight:bold;">1</span>,<span style="color:blue; font-weight:bold;">450</span>,<span style="color:blue; font-weight:bold;">100</span>,<span style="color:green; font-weight:bold;">'cms'</span>,<span style="color:maroon; font-weight:bold;">'0'</span>); return false;"&gt;{l s='Your text' mod='opartajaxpopup'}&lt;/a&gt;<br />
	</div>
	<span style="color:red; font-weight:bold;">{l s='1 is your CMS ID, you can find it on the cms admin list' mod='opartajaxpopup'}</span><br />
	<span style="color:blue; font-weight:bold;">{l s='450 is the width of your popup' mod='opartajaxpopup' mod='opartajaxpopup'}</span><br />
	<span style="color:blue; font-weight:bold;">{l s='100 is the height of your popup' mod='opartajaxpopup' mod='opartajaxpopup'}</span><br />
	<span style="color:green; font-weight:bold;">{l s='cms is using for specify to the script what kind of content is expected' mod='opartajaxpopup'}</span><br />
	<span style="color:maroon; font-weight:bold;">{l s='0 is using for specify if your popup will be responsive or not (0=no, 1=yes)' mod='opartajaxpopup'}</span><br />
</fieldset>
